"image": "", "category": "Rituals", "excerpt": "Discover the deep spiritual meaning behind the worship of Lord Ganesha and why Ganesh Chaturthi is celebrated with such fervor.", "content": "<p>Lord Ganesha, the elephant-headed deity, is the remover of obstacles and the god of beginnings. Worshiping Him before any new venture ensures success and prosperity...</p><p>Ganesh Chaturthi marks the birth of the Lord, and it is a time for communal prayer, stunning decorations, and heartfelt devotion.</p>", "date": "2026-03-10", "created_at": "2026-03-10T13:33:02.357Z"}}, {"model": "core.blog", "pk": 2, "fields": {"title": "Daily Vedic Rituals for a Peaceful Home", "slug": "daily-vedic-rituals-for-a-peaceful-home", "image": "", "category": "Lifestyle", "excerpt": "A guide to simple yet powerful Vedic practices you can perform every day to maintain a positive and peaceful vibration in your living space.", "content": "<p>In the Vedic tradition, our home is a sacred space. Simple actions like lighting a diya (lamp), chanting specific mantras, and maintaining cleanliness can transform the energy of your home...</p>", "date": "2026-03-10", "created_at": "2026-03-10T13:33:02.358Z"}}, {"model": "core.blog", "pk": 3, "fields": {"title": "Understanding the Power of Mantras", "slug": "understanding-the-power-of-mantras", "image": "", "category": "Knowledge", "excerpt": "Explore the science of sound and how Vedic mantras can positively affect the mind, body, and soul.", "content": "<p>Mantras are not just religious chants; they are sacred sounds with specific frequencies. When chanted correctly, they resonate with the cosmic vibrations, bringing mental clarity and spiritual awakening...</p>", "date": "2026-03-10", "created_at": "2026-03-10T13:33:02.358Z"}}, {"model": "core.pujacategory", "pk": 1, "fields": {"name": "Prosperity", "slug": "prosperity", "description": "Rituals for wealth and success.", "display_order": 0, "is_active": true, "created_at": "2026-03-10T12:41:49.008Z"}}, {"mod